FLASK FRAMEWORK DETAILS
=============================================

Flask is a micro frameworkused for website and Web API development.Being a micro framework means it has a simple core and it is easily
extendable. 
Flask is using the Jinja2 template engine with works with WSGI tookit. WSGI stands for Web Server Gateway Interface.A standard interface
between web servers and web applications. 
Flask is a framework with batteries included. In many cases, even Python is mentioned as a programming language with batteries included.
This means the Flask framework supports building extensions.
